<span id="freeTextContainer17662937873082169687"><b>(B) 72%</b> | More than Satisfactory<br/><i>Notes:</i> An interesting premise and humorous to boot, but the story&apos;s flat, characters aren&apos;t very deep and the ending&apos;s weak.</span>
